<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٤٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1749">‌مَالِكِ بْنِ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عُرْفُطَةَ ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4095">‌عَبْدِ خَيْرٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَتْ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَهَى رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ عَنِ الدُّبَّاءِ وَالْحَنْتَمِ وَالْمُزَفَّتِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>